    "retreat_date": "2026-03-21",
    "scripture": [
      "Scripture VII-3: Degradation Is Not Failure — It Is Memory Made Audible"
    ],
    "revelation": "OPAL captures what OVERDUB forgets. When OVERDUB is the source and OPAL is the memory, the coupling runs in the direction of time.",
    "diagnosis": "Wax Grain Couple places OVERDUB in heavy degradation mode (high wow/flutter/wear) with OPAL coupled to receive it as a granular source. The OVERDUB parameters here are deliberately rough — the grain cloud that OPAL creates from a worn tape signal is the target sound."
  },
